{"tid":431450,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有個蠢老母真係慘過食屎","createTime":"2017-10-10T16:49:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-12T10:42:06.000Z","uid":6546,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"d7fddec47019d2d3bdcc3433f1e4605af41100c7","tid":431450,"uid":6546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T16:49:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/004337_38c94d6bdc166c14ede12798b5d39c5b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F004337_38c94d6bdc166c14ede12798b5d39c5b.jpg&h=207353dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢個唔知咩產品佢買咗七百幾蚊<br />\n話幹細胞又乜又成<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/004424_221d55a87822e90117b8b6a50a777530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F004424_221d55a87822e90117b8b6a50a777530.jpg&h=4d1688c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上網查下咩料咁勁<br />\n點知$25x就買到<br />\nJeunesse呢個牌子係傳銷嚟<br />\n<br />\n諗住同佢講俾人搵笨，點知佢話呢啲係假嘅<br />\n<br />\n佢之前已經俾人昆咗10幾萬<br />\n<br />\n抵我公屋仔一世做窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無人明我感受<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/11/004935_ed839ef7cd941db8068525e4acadd551.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F11%2F004935_ed839ef7cd941db8068525e4acadd551.jpg&h=0a506352&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9871e9814f201a11faec85947911d2e250d6d061","tid":431450,"uid":123647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-10T17:01:20.000Z","msg":"幾舊水已經算少<br />\n<br />\n有啲老母成副身家比敦倫金班仆街吸哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0f30dc84a745c1da591f9d4b65f175f34c44aaf","tid":431450,"uid":98878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,